casebody.data:
Estate of Oliver, Appellant, v. Dewey et al.; Liberty Mutual Fire Insurance Company, Appellee.

[Cite as Estate of Oliver v. Dewey (2001), 93 Ohio St.3d 1231.]

(No. 00-2123 Submitted October 31, 2001 Decided December 12, 2001.) Joseph L. Coticchia, for appellant. Reid, Berry, Marshall & Wargo, Timothy T. Reid and P. Kohl Schneider, for appellee.

The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
